parameters:
We have 112 pekomiko fruits... 13kg of uraraice... Oh, it seems
we don't have enough chitoroa... Sigh... If we make a mistake in
the inspection, the landlady will get really angry...

After making that, make this... Then make that over there...
Phew...! This feeling of challenging the limits of cooking...
It's irresistible!

Ah... I need to restock the beef fillet steak. I wonder if I can
ask Foil-kun...?
Welcome. It's 10G per night. Will you be staying?

Do you not even have 10G? You must be worried about the future...
Well, the world is full of compassion, so you can stay for
free...!!

Don't you feel like the books in the store are more interesting
than usual?
Hmm... I look beautiful today, don't I...

She gets angry when you talk to her while she's admiring herself
in the mirror. It's about time for the quest though...
